ustively scan rows/columns or enumerate every option. Test one idea, read the result, then decide.", "kind": "tool", "inContext": true}, {"label": "THINKING", "content": "Good, the 7 green blocks are converted. The view now shows mostly sky blue with some black cutouts. Let me check if there are any remaining green blocks by scanning the current view and then scrolling to check other areas.", "kind": "reasoning", "inContext": false}, {"label": "ASSISTANT", "content": "World model: Converted 7 green blocks. Need to check for remaining ones across the full map.\nPlan: Check current view for green blocks, then scan remaining areas efficiently.", "kind": "reasoning", "inContext": true}, {"label": "TOOL CALL: python", "content": "<tool_call>\n<function=python>\n<parameter=code>\nseg = current_frame.segmentation\ngreens = [n for n in seg['nodes'] if n['color'] == 'N']\nprint(f\"Green blocks in view: {len(greens)}\")\n\n# Check all colors\ncolors = {}\nfor n in seg['nodes']:\n    colors[n['color']] = colors.get(n['color'], 0) + n['pixels']\nprint(f\"Colors: {colors}\")\n\n# Scroll right to check for more\naction(['RIGHT', 'RIGHT', 'RIGHT', 'RIGHT', 'RIGHT'])\n</parameter>\n</function>\n</tool_call>", "kind": "tool", "inContext": true}, {"label": "TOOL RESULT: python", "content": "Green blocks in view: 0\nColors: {'B': 1818, 'S': 2056, 'G': 150, 'b': 6, 'Y': 2, 'p': 8, 'W': 56}", "kind": "tool", "inContext": true}], "hasExactModelContext": false, "requestIndexWithinTurn": null, "messageCount": 0}}}